queries.query: Select Id, %vlocity_namespace%__Type__c, %vlocity_namespace%__SubType__c from %vlocity_namespace%__OmniScript__c WHERE %vlocity_namespace%__IsActive__c = true AND %vlocity_namespace%__IsProcedure__c = true

Select Id, %vlocity_namespace%__Type__c, %vlocity_namespace%__SubType__c, %vlocity_namespace%__Language__c, %vlocity_namespace%__IsLwcEnabled__c from %vlocity_namespace%__OmniScript__c WHERE %vlocity_namespace%__IsActive__c = true AND %vlocity_namespace%__IsProcedure__c = false
